Create active task folders under `tasks/todo/` with the format `YYYY-MM-DD-description/`.

Quick-start summary:
- use one active task folder per effort;
- keep `task_plan.md`, `findings.md`, and `progress.md` current throughout the session;
- move completed tasks to `tasks/archive/` with the same folder name.

Each active task folder should contain:
- `task_plan.md`
- `findings.md`
- `progress.md`

Source of truth:
- detailed workflow rules live in `AGENTS.md`;
- adjacent planning surfaces (`TODO.md`, `implementation_notes.md`, `CHANGELOG.md`, `Bugs.md`) must stay synchronized when relevant;
- root-level `task_plan.md`, `findings.md`, and `progress.md` are historical artifacts, not the current active-task workflow.
